snippet.textDisplay:
I realise how whether through nature, nurture or preconceived ideas about what anything smells like, people really are different when he said he smelt garlic from durians.

To Asians born and BRED, the smell of durians is fragrant, not smelly.

Hope they enjoyed the visit !
